{
  "stem": "1511.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I told him who I am, that I am going here and here, and I have a sister living there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came to sell things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so now I'm going back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, he started talking to me, that maybe I'll go with them because there was something then that England and Russia made an agreement, that they're going to let their people out.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these people can go to England, that was in Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they took only the Goyim, not the Hedin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this guy got himself a little paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, you could make for money, everything in there, and the other one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they both went on that boat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, not yet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I said goodbye to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I went down in Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they, I don't know where they were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he told me this story later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Mendel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His real name is Lippa-- Leo, Lippa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in there, for some kind of reason-- and I'll tell you later the reason-- that he-- he was caught in something and he had to change his name.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So for a few ruble, you change your name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came to [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The city was the first where I went then, is Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I had to go to Samarkand to see my girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when I came to Tashkent, I bought tobacco.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Chkalov, because it was very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Uzbeks were taking all kind of opiums and all kind, and the tobacco they like, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as I went, the first thing on the market, I want to eat something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's little guys-- they call them [NON-ENGLISH]-- they grabbed that bag with the tobacco from me right away, away.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
